value.name: Grand Abounami - Wikipedia
value.snippet: Length. 159 km (99 mi) Basin features. Progression. Lawa → Maroni → Atlantic Ocean. The Grand Abounami is a river in western French Guiana. It is a right tributary of the Lawa (the upper course of the Maroni ). It is 159 km (99 mi) long. [1]
